SimpleListActivity is a project that illustrates simple lists (in lecture slides)

Themes is a project that shows how to create themes and switch between them.

MyList illustrates simple array adapters.

MyListCustomRow illustrates how to build a custom row.

MylistCustomAdpater illustrates how to extend an adapter.

CopyDbDemo show how to copy a db into your app via assets.

SaveDataFile simply shows how to write to the internal memory.

SearchableDictionary is the Android sample project.

TodoDatabase is Lars Vogel's demo.
